rows.label: qst001302_msg0002
rows.name: That could only be Bontalbo's cooking!

rows.label: qst001302_msg0003
rows.name:
Ah, thanks for delivering that... Salted
Brog Sauté is kind of my life-blood.

rows.label: qst001302_msg0004
rows.name:
I heard they had some problems with
the supply of Folta. But it looks like
it's all sorted out now!

rows.label: qst001302_msg0005
rows.name:
Huh? Just warning you, I'm not gonna
share this. It's one of the only things
makes my life worth living here.

rows.label: qst001302_msg0006
rows.name:
Why don't you run off back to Bontalbo
and convey my thanks.

rows.label: qst001302_msg0101
rows.name:
Don't bother me when I'm
getting ready to enjoy a delicious
Salted Brog Sauté!

rows.label: qst001302_msg0102
rows.name: Just give my thanks to Bontalbo, okay?
